{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775864515728,"sessionID":"ses_2863cec50ffemPwHwFVZrIdh3Z","part":{"id":"prt_d79c60c6e0017A80W0WC9fyotA","messageID":"msg_d79c5f169001Z7pITKbnooQ08W","sessionID":"ses_2863cec50ffemPwHwFVZrIdh3Z","type":"tool","tool":"edit","callID":"toolu_tool-0dfaa15e927246e6b530f274727be95c","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-019/CHANGE.md","newString":"# AR-019 — CLI 二进制入口 (4 binaries)\n\n## Metadata\n- **AR**: AR-019\n- **Title**: CLI 二进制入口 (4 binaries)\n- **Module**: cmd\n- **Language**: Go\n- **Size**: M\n- **Status**: Completed\n\n## Description\n\nImplemented 4 CLI binary entry points for managing AgentRuntime and CodeInterpreter Kubernetes resources:\n\n1. **agentcube** - Main unified CLI with subcommands for managing both resource types\n2. **agent-runtime** - Dedicated CLI for AgentRuntime resource operations\n3. **code-interpreter** - Dedicated CLI for CodeInterpreter resource operations\n4. **agentcube-util** - Utility CLI for validation, diagnostics, and completion generation\n\n## Dependencies\n\n- github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/cli\n- github.com/spf13/cobra\n- gopkg.in/yaml.v3\n- k8s.io/client-go\n- k8s.io/apimachinery\n\n## Related Changes\n\nNone\n\n## Implementation Notes\n\nAll binaries build successfully and support the following features:\n\n- Common flags: --kubeconfig, --namespace, --output\n- CRUD operations: list, get, create, update, delete, watch\n- Output formats: table, json, yaml\n- Shell completion: bash, zsh, fish, powershell\n- Error handling with user-friendly messages\n\n## Deferred Items\n\nThe following items were deferred for future implementation:\n\n- Unit tests for all binaries\n- Integration tests\n- Static analysis (go vet, gofmt)\n- Makefile build targets\n- README documentation for each binary\n- Environment variable support testing\n- Project documentation updates","oldString":"# AR