or all binaries\n- Integration tests\n- Static analysis (go vet, gofmt)\n- Makefile build targets\n- README documentation for each binary\n- Environment variable support testing\n- Project documentation updates","additions":38,"deletions":4},"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-019/CHANGE.md","time":{"start":1775864515710,"end":1775864515724}}}}
